## Priority: Critical

Slot contracts exist via `defineSlot()` but there is no way to render slot content in templates. `v-slot` is rejected with "not supported yet". Without this, component composition is severely limited.

## Scope

- Parse `v-slot:name` and `#name` shorthand on `<template>` tags
- Default slot support (`v-slot:default` or `#default`)
- Pass slot content to component render function
- Generate slot rendering in client and server codegen

## Example

```html
<MyLayout>
  <template #header>
    <h1>Title</h1>
  </template>
  <p>Default content</p>
</MyLayout>
```

## Files to modify

- `src/compiler/template/builder_validate.mbt` — accept v-slot
- `src/compiler/template/builder_attrs.mbt` — parse slot binding
- `src/compiler/codegen/attrs_component.mbt` — emit slot content
- `src/compiler/common/types.mbt` — add slot info to TemplateElement